== Decision ==
The dynamic CID update message symbols are absent, while DTLS 1.3 ACK, unified header sequence-number, record-number encryption, and anti-replay paths are present in source. Current CMake cache also has WOLFSSL_DTLS13=no and WOLFSSL_DTLS_CID=no, so built executable tests for the missing dynamic CID messages are not available in this build tree.
